document_title: Cosmetic (silicon) breast implant rupture: causes, signs and treatment
subsection_content:
Saline and silicone gel implants are designed to last for many years. However, they will not last forever. The silicone shell that holds the saline solution and silicone gel will eventually wear off, leading to minor leaks or ruptured breast implants.
Breast implant manufacturers claim that their products have an average lifespan of at least 10 years. However, there are still cases where breast implants last for a longer or shorter time.
